Design Description
AnimeLoop has a vibrant, modern design for anime fans:
Colors: Dark background with bright accent colors for titles and buttons
Typography: Bold headings for series titles, readable body text
Layout: Grid structure for featured anime, lists, and weekly schedules
Imagery: High-quality banners and thumbnails
Interactivity: DUB/SUB toggles, episode play buttons, hover effects
Future Improvements
Add backend for community logins and user profiles
Implement search and filter functionality
Optimize SEO and performance
Add ratings, comments, and user playlists
Contributing
